creator: Gympass
descriptionHtml:
Gympass is a corporate wellness service that wants to help you find an activity to love. You can change your routine everyday or stick with what you like best, it's up to you! With more than 2,000 venues across the UK and more than 40,000 worldwide, it's easy to get started!

- Create an account for free
- Explore our network of venues
- Purchase the plan that best suits you
- Check in on arrival at session and have fun!

With Gympass you can choose to do Yoga, Crossfit, Swimming, Skiing, Ju-Jitsu or even relax at the spa, the options are endless. One monthly membership that offers all this with no cancellation or membership fees, what else are you waiting for?
descriptionShort: One membership, more than 40,000 gyms to discover worldwide, this is Gympass!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Staying active has never been more important. That's why we made it possible for you to do it all from home!

Join our fitness partners in fun live-streamed classes or access a variety of partner apps specialized in online fitness and wellness.

Discover this and a lot more in our latest update!

title: Gympass

creator: Gympass
descriptionHtml:
One membership offering access to a range of different gyms and studios at a competitive price.

Gympass is a corporate wellness program with a mission to help you find an activity to love. You can change your routine every day or stick with what you like best ⁠— it's up to you! With thousands of gyms and studios across the US and more than 40,000 worldwide, it's easy to find something and get started!

- Create an account for free
- Explore our network of gyms and studios
- Purchase the plan that suits you best
- Check in once you arrive at your workout destination

With Gympass, you can choose to do Yoga, CrossFit, Swimming, Kickboxing, and even Rock Climbing — the options are endless. One monthly membership offers all this with no cancellation or membership fees... what are you waiting for?
descriptionShort: One membership to more than 40,000 gyms and studios around the world.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

Join our fitness partners in fun live-streamed classes or access a variety of partner apps specialized in online fitness and wellness. Or what about booking a personal training session with your favorite trainer?

Discover this and a lot more in our latest update!

title: Gympass

creator: Gympass
descriptionHtml:
We partner with your company to offer flexible plans that let you stay active and focus on your well-being. 🏃🏼‍♀️ Each of our plans gives you access to a worldwide network of fitness partners. 🌍

You can book a class at the nearest gym during your lunch break 🤸🏾‍♂️, join an audio-guided running session at the park 🎧, get started with 1-on-1 online sessions 🧑🏻‍💻, or spice up your Sunday night with a cooking class. 🥕 Do whatever makes you feel good.

It’s all in one app, with one single membership. No strings attached. It’s that easy. 🥳

Here’s everything that is waiting for you:

🏢 Gyms and studios all over the world: Visit a different one every day if you like, or find your favorite one.

📱Wellness apps: Discover therapy sessions, nutrition plans tailored to your needs, and even financial well-being.

💻 Live-streamed classes and on-demand workouts: You choose the when and where. Enjoy Gympass on-the-go.

👩🏽‍💻 Personal training sessions: Get to know personal trainers from all over the country through 1-on-1 online sessions.

📲 Download the app to get started on your wellness journey. Cancel anytime for free.
descriptionShort: A corporate benefit for your body 🏋🏽‍♀️, mind 🧘🏻‍♂️, and mood 💆🏽‍♀️.

title: Gympass

creator: Gympass
descriptionHtml:
We partner with your company to offer flexible plans that let you stay active and focus on your well-being. 🏃🏼‍♀️ Each of our plans gives you access to a worldwide network of fitness partners. 🌍

You can book a class at the nearest gym during your lunch break 🤸🏾‍♂️, join an audio-guided running session at the park 🎧, get started with 1-on-1 online sessions 🧑🏻‍💻, or spice up your Sunday night with a cooking class. 🥕 Do whatever makes you feel good.

It’s all in one app, with one single membership. No strings attached. It’s that easy. 🥳

Here’s everything that is waiting for you:

🏢 Gyms and studios all over the world: Visit a different one every day if you like, or find your favorite one.

📱Wellness apps: Discover therapy sessions, nutrition plans tailored to your needs, and even financial well-being.

💻 Live-streamed classes and on-demand workouts: You choose the when and where. Enjoy Gympass on-the-go.

👩🏽‍💻 Personal training sessions: Get to know personal trainers from all over the country through 1-on-1 online sessions.

📲 Download the app to get started on your wellness journey. Cancel anytime for free.
descriptionShort: A corporate benefit for your body 🏋🏽‍♀️, mind 🧘🏻‍♂️, and mood 💆🏽‍♀️.

title: Gympass

creator: Gympass
descriptionHtml:
We partner with your company to offer flexible plans that let you stay active and focus on your well-being. 🏃🏼‍♀️ Each of our plans gives you access to a worldwide network of fitness and wellness partners. 🌍

You can book a class at the nearest gym during your lunch break 🤸🏾‍♂️, join an audio-guided running session at the park 🎧, get started with 1-on-1 online sessions 🧑🏻‍💻, or spice up your Sunday night with a cooking class. 🥕 Do whatever makes you feel good.

It’s all in one app, with one single membership. No strings attached. It’s that easy. 🥳

Here’s everything that is waiting for you:

🏢 Gyms and studios all over the world: Visit a different one every day if you like, or find your favorite one.

📱Wellness apps: Discover therapy sessions, nutrition plans tailored to your needs, and even financial well-being.

💻 Live-streamed classes and on-demand workouts: You choose the when and where. Enjoy Gympass on-the-go.

👩🏽‍💻 Personal training sessions: Get to know personal trainers from all over the country through 1-on-1 online sessions.

📲 Download the app to get started on your wellness journey. Cancel anytime for free.
descriptionShort: A corporate benefit for your body 🏋🏽‍♀️, mind 🧘🏻‍♂️, and mood 💆🏽‍♀️.

title: Gympass

creator: Gympass
descriptionHtml:
We partner with your company to offer flexible plans that let you stay active and focus on your well-being. 🏃🏼‍♀️ Each of our plans gives you access to a worldwide network of fitness and wellness partners. 🌍

You can book a class at the nearest gym during your lunch break 🤸🏾‍♂️, join an audio-guided running session at the park 🎧, get started with 1-on-1 online sessions 🧑🏻‍💻, or spice up your Sunday night with a cooking class. 🥕 Do whatever makes you feel good.

It’s all in one app, with one single membership. No strings attached. It’s that easy. 🥳

Here’s everything that is waiting for you:

🏢 Gyms and studios all over the world: Visit a different one every day if you like, or find your favorite one.

📱Wellness apps: Discover therapy sessions, nutrition plans tailored to your needs, and even financial well-being.

💻 Live-streamed classes and on-demand workouts: You choose the when and where. Enjoy Gympass on-the-go.

👩🏽‍💻 Personal training sessions: Get to know personal trainers from all over the country through 1-on-1 online sessions.

📲 Download the app to get started on your wellness journey. Cancel anytime for free.

You can book a class at the nearest gym during your lunch break 🤸🏾‍♂️, join an audio-guided running session at the park 🎧, get started with 1-on-1 online sessions 🧑🏻‍💻, or spice up your Sunday night with a cooking class. 🥕 Do whatever makes you feel good.

It’s all in one app, with one single membership. No strings attached. It’s that easy. 🥳

Here’s everything that is waiting for you:

🏢 Gyms and studios all over the world: Visit a different one every day if you like, or find your favorite one.

📱Wellness apps: Discover therapy sessions, nutrition plans tailored to your needs, and even financial well-being.

💻 Live-streamed classes and on-demand workouts: You choose the when and where. Enjoy Gympass on-the-go.

👩🏽‍💻 Personal training sessions: Get to know personal trainers from all over the country through 1-on-1 online sessions.

📲 Download the app to get started on your wellness journey. Cancel anytime for free.

You can book a class at the nearest gym during your lunch break 🤸🏾‍♂️, join an audio-guided running session at the park 🎧, get started with 1-on-1 online sessions 🧑🏻‍💻, or spice up your Sunday night with a cooking class. 🥕 Do whatever makes you feel good.

It’s all in one app, with one single membership. No strings attached. It’s that easy. 🥳

Here’s everything that is waiting for you:

🏢 Gyms and studios all over the world: Visit a different one every day if you like, or find your favorite one.

📱Wellness apps: Discover therapy sessions, nutrition plans tailored to your needs, and even financial well-being.

💻 Live-streamed classes and on-demand workouts: You choose the when and where. Enjoy Gympass on-the-go.

👩🏽‍💻 Personal training sessions: Get to know personal trainers from all over the country through 1-on-1 online sessions.

📲 Download the app to get started on your wellness journey. Cancel anytime for free.

You can book a class at the nearest gym during your lunch break 🤸🏾‍♂️, join an audio-guided running session at the park 🎧, get started with 1-on-1 online sessions 🧑🏻‍💻, or spice up your Sunday night with a cooking class. 🥕 Do whatever makes you feel good.

It’s all in one app, with one single membership. No strings attached. It’s that easy. 🥳

Here’s everything that is waiting for you:

🏢 Gyms and studios all over the world: Visit a different one every day if you like, or find your favorite one.

📱Wellness apps: Discover therapy sessions, nutrition plans tailored to your needs, and even financial well-being.

💻 Live-streamed classes and on-demand workouts: You choose the when and where. Enjoy Gympass on-the-go.

👩🏽‍💻 Personal training sessions: Get to know personal trainers from all over the country through 1-on-1 online sessions.

📲 Download the app to get started on your wellness journey. Cancel anytime for free.

We partner with your company to offer flexible plans that let you stay active and focus on your well-being. 🏃🏼‍♀️ Each of our plans gives you access to a worldwide network of fitness and wellness partners. 🌍

You can book a class at the nearest gym during your lunch break 🤸🏾‍♂️, join an audio-guided running session at the park 🎧, get started with 1-on-1 online sessions 🧑🏻‍💻, or spice up your Sunday night with a cooking class. 🥕 Do whatever makes you feel good.

It’s all in one app, with one single membership. No strings attached. It’s that easy. 🥳

Here’s everything that is waiting for you:

🏢 Gyms and studios all over the world: Visit a different one every day if you like, or find your favorite one.

📱Wellness apps: Discover therapy sessions, nutrition plans tailored to your needs, and even financial well-being.

💻 Live-streamed classes and on-demand workouts: You choose the when and where. Enjoy Gympass on-the-go.

👩🏽‍💻 Personal training sessions: Get to know personal trainers from all over the country through 1-on-1 online sessions.

📲 Download the app to get started on your wellness journey. Cancel anytime for free.
descriptionShort: A corporate benefit for your body 🏋🏽‍♀️, mind 🧘🏻‍♂️, and mood 💆🏽‍♀️.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
With this version, we’ve improved our app performance and we’ve also fixed some bugs. We know we can get better, but rest assured we are working on improving your experience every day.

How about you download this version and get your check-in done for today?

creator: Gympass
descriptionHtml:
Gympass is now Wellhub! Offered by your company, Wellhub helps you check in with your wellbeing every day by connecting you to the best partners for fitness, mindfulness, therapy, nutrition, and sleep.

Access gyms, studios, classes, individualized coaching, and top-rated wellness apps, all included in one subscription designed to cost less than each individual partner.

Popular gyms & studios: Visit your favorite fitness clubs or try something new every day with hundreds of activities like swimming, spinning, yoga, pilates, CrossFit, climbing, and dance.

Wellness apps: Instantly access premium apps for sleep, meditation, and nutritional guidance to relieve stress and promote self-care.

On-demand classes: Work out and stay well anywhere with live-streamed classes, on-demand workouts, and individualized wellness coaching.

Join millions of eligible employees worldwide by starting a wellbeing journey with Wellhub. Enjoy risk-free with no enrollment or cancellation fees.
